    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the top and bottom off your <strong>pomegranate</strong>, then slice into quarters and add the <strong>pomegranate quarters</strong> to a large bowl filled with <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Tip: This helps prevent mess and makes separating the pith easier!</p><p>Separate the <strong>pomegranate seeds </strong>from the <strong>white pith </strong>and discard the pith, then drain the <strong>pomegranate seeds</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
