      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pitta[s] has had 10 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>walnuts</strong> to the other side</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>to the walnuts</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 3-4 min or until the walnuts are toasted and the pitta is crispy – this is your <strong>za'atar & Greek cheese manakeesh and toasted walnuts</strong></p>",
