    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>most</strong> of your <strong>pomegranate seeds </strong>(save some for a garnish!) in a large bowl with <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>harissa</strong> <strong>dressing</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and toss it all together – this is your <strong>harissa & pomegranate salad</strong></p>",
