    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>za'atar & Greek cheese manakeesh </strong>into thin triangles</p><p>Serve the <strong>harissa & pomegranate salad</strong> topped with the<strong> za'atar & Greek cheese manakeesh triangles</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> remaining pomegranate seeds</strong>,<strong> toasted walnuts </strong>and the <strong>remaining harissa dressing</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
